            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-1a.1" xml:lang="en">The minister of justice (?) of Lu entrusted (a ritual) to Yan You in Jun Chu (?), </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-1a.2" xml:lang="en">(Yan You) said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en">Clean up (the ritual premises?)! </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en">Sikou will come to visit me.” </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en">The followers did clean up, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en">but the minister of justice did not come. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en">Yan You left. </seg>
                </p>

            <p>
                    <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-2a.1" xml:lang="en">The minister [of justice sent people to ask him] </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-2a.2" xml:lang="en">"Where are you going?" </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-2a.3" xml:lang="en">Yan you said: </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-2a.4" xml:lang="en">“To give food to someone without performing the ritual (?) with him, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-2a.5" xml:lang="en">This is the way that merchants and craftsmen (?) are fed. </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-2a.6" xml:lang="en">I, Yan, cultivate my virtuous conduct, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-2a.7" xml:lang="en">(so) to receive from you the food of merchants and craftsmen </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-2a.8" xml:lang="en">is unbecoming towards me, (?) </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-2a.9" xml:lang="en">and a waste for you, </seg>
               <seg corresp="#KR2p0073_tls_001-2a.10" xml:lang="en">therefore why should I stay?” </seg>
                </p>

         </div>
